id":497324,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:33:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有排都未得<br />\n<br />\n偶有佳作<br />\n但最top果堆都未及林夕既average level<br />\n<br />\n林夕有一排好想幫佢上位<br />\n奈何佢既水平都係上唔到</blockquote><br />\n最top都不及average 又過左啲，林夕作太多歌，唔少都一般般</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都岩<br />\n藝術家係咁架啦<br />\n遇到自己鍾意既歌手同題材先出真功夫<br />\n佢自己都認有時交行貨<br />\n但動真格真係勁到痴線</blockquote><br />\n佢幫juno作d詞真係好撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n創作職業都要交貨，交貨真係唔可以首首都慢慢雕琢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nyes<br />\n而且有時係對方要求你唔好寫得咁有深度<br />\n因為俾錢果個老細自己都睇唔明<br />\n仲要對你件作品意見多多，改完又改<br />\n做創作行業就明白"},{"pid":"43fc6d671ca65e7d4d720bba9975caa7b2ae3c5f","tid":497324,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢可能用詞無林夕咁有文彩，但佢d歌詞係好有感覺<br />\n我特別鍾意佢為周國賢作詞（時空，年輕人們）仲有周柏豪（還記得）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實自己鍾意就得<br />\n夠有人話黃霑屌打全部<br />\n笑下咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdc2159e0b853664ca6d29abc6ad9b49cf09803","tid":497324,"uid":161011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:55:27.000Z","msg":"希望佢繼續進步，但林夕係神級，無人能及，亦代表左一個時代。"},{"pid":"e471d62826a1ba89c0ca6d20811acadf87ef6900","tid":497324,"uid":23392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T17:00:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搶左下屬老婆個個？</blockquote><br />\n你望下月球下的人曲詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda942d4382786dcedf9ae5b5b7e2418fa9305e4","tid":497324,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"連陳詠謙都未去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hk